semanticMarkup.io.input

Class GenericFileVolumeReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • semanticMarkup.io.input.AbstractFileVolumeReader
      • semanticMarkup.io.input.GenericFileVolumeReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVolumeReader, IValidationRunListener

    public class GenericFileVolumeReader
extends AbstractFileVolumeReader
implements IValidationRunListener
    GenericFileVolumeReader reads takes a filePath to check whether there is input available at the given format for any of XMLVolumeReader, TaxonxVolumeReader or DocWordVolumeReader. If there is it delegates the actual reading to the appropriate reader
